{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2645df4039","title":"关于召开第二次防治血吸虫病会议的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"086f89f4d6","index":1,"year":1956,"month":3,"day":5,"articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"307f4dd8d3","index":0,"year":1956,"month":3,"day":3,"articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"e4b274686d","index":2,"year":1956,"month":3,"day":7,"articleId":"2645df4039"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"a7b8259acf","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时在中共中央副秘书长、中央办公厅主任。"},{"id":"cc56b95eeb","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"柯庆施，当时任中共上海市委第一书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"309d164d73","type":"title","text":"关于召开第二次防治血吸虫病会议的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"a7b8259acf","type":"paragraph","text":"送中央卫生部徐运北同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"cc56b95eeb","type":"paragraph","text":"原定今年三月在上海召开第二次防治血吸虫病的会议，是否按期召开？准备情形如何？望告。开会时可邀秉志先生前往参加","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"6e751be495","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"9f6296f48a","type":"paragraph","text":"三月三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"d50ff15409","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]本篇一写在中国科学院动物研究室水生动物研究专家秉志1956年2月28日为转送他给毛泽东的信而写给刘少奇的信上。秉志在给毛泽东的信中提出，消灭钉螺用土理不行，必须用火楚烧，以期永绝后患。本篇二写在中共四川省委防治钩虫病、血吸虫病五人小组办公室1956年3月2日给中央防治血吸虫病九人小组办公室的电报上。本篇三写在卫生部副部长徐运北1956年3月5日关于召开防治血吸虫病会议问题给毛泽东的信上。尚昆同志：","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"1d5aa448d0","type":"paragraph","text":"请你电话告知上海柯庆施同志和中央卫生部徐运北同志，今年三月召开第二次防治血吸虫病会议的时候，应当邀请福建、广东、广西、四川等有血吸虫和钩虫病的省区派出代表到上海参加会议，并问他们此次会议何日召开，有无准备？","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"4ae3b5a88a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"27fc9fa195","type":"paragraph","text":"三月五日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"24a3312acc","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"944476a8b5","type":"paragraph","text":"中央卫生部徐运北同志：","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"d626f338db","type":"paragraph","text":"除长江中下游六省外，其他已发现血吸虫病的省份如四川、广东、福建等也应当请他们派代表参加，请与村庆施同志商处。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"dd99662843","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"48372713e9","type":"paragraph","text":"三月七日","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"73819b0756","type":"paragraph","text":"会议除讨论血吸虫病为主要任务以外，钩虫病及其他最严重的疾病也宜加以讨论。会议应当订定下一次会议，下半年再开一次会议（即每年开会两次）也就可以了。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"},{"id":"a42f306450","type":"paragraph","text":"1956年3月，毛泽东和中医研究院第一任院长鲁之俊握手。","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039"}],"page":{"id":"90c5397ce5","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"2645df4039","start":238,"end":240}}}},"__N_SSG":true}